children.name: business1
children.text: You're right. I'll just be on my way.

children.name: business3
children.text: I need to get in. Just let me pass.
children.response: How did you get this far, anyway? Did you talk to Prip? And is Prap still somehow employed?

children.name: notime
children.text: Yes, Prap is still working. And Prip said I could go straight up.
children.response: Really? Well, lucky you. It's just through this passage. Have a nice stay!
